</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Range Rover 最新旗艦車抵港，極簡線條豪華內籠 + 混合動力選擇</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/25/land-rover-range-rover/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=land-rover-range-rover</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jun 2022 03:31:01 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><category><![CDATA[land rover]]></category><category><![CDATA[range rover]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1106761</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Land Rover 最新旗艦車型 Range Rover 正式抵港，推出多款混能車型；而使用「Reimagi [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Land Rover 最新旗艦車型 Range Rover 正式抵港，推出多款混能車型；而使用「Reimagine」的純電動車型將於 2024 年推出，實現首輛 Range Rover 的零排放。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Range Rover 採用經典的下切車頂線及上升門檻線設計，配合短前懸船型風格車，形成分體式尾門。車身線條流暢連貫的 Range Rover 車門框線圓潤，在特殊設計，使用內嵌式平整車窗及隱藏式照明，令車身一體成形。除了令外觀更吸引外，特殊設計更令 Range Rover 的風阻系數降至 0.3Cd，成為全球空氣動力性能最佳的豪華 SUV 車型。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171105-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1106778" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171105-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171105-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171105-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171105-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171105-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171105-2048x1153.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171634-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1106780" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171634-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171634-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171634-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171634-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171634-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171634-2048x1153.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Range Rover 搭載 1,600W Meridian 音響系統，在 4 個主要的頭枕內安裝了額外的 20W 揚聲器，並配備主動式降噪揚聲器，營造高端耳機般的音響效果。在第三代主動降噪系統下，Range Rover 能監測車輪震動、胎噪及傳入車廂的引擎噪音，再透過系統內 35 個揚聲器發出降噪指示，有效減少噪音，為駕駛者及乘客帶來靜謐空間。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171344-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1106781" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171344-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171344-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171344-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171344-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171344-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171344-2048x1153.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171734-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1106782" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171734-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171734-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171734-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171734-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171734-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171734-2048x1153.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171840-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1106783" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171840-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171840-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171840-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171840-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171840-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171840-2048x1153.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Range Rover 的高級空氣淨化系統（CabinAirPurificationPro）採用二氧化碳管理系統及 PM2.5 過濾和雙重 nanoeTMX 技術，有效減少過敏原、SARS-CoV-2 等細菌及病毒，更可消除大部分異味，將微粒即場淨化，確保前後排的乘客都有保障。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171310-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1106785" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171310-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171310-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171310-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171310-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171310-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171310-2048x1153.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171542-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1106786" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171542-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171542-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171542-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171542-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171542-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171542-2048x1153.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171450-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1106787" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171450-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171450-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171450-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171450-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171450-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171450-2048x1153.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">以 MLA-Flex 車體結構製造的 Range Rover 提供標準和長陣版型號，設有 4 座、5 座或 7 座位作選擇。Range Rover 有多款電能動力系統，具高效輕混能（mild-hybrid）和插電式混合動力（plug-in hybrid）系統，而純電版則於 2024 年發表，方便不同需要的車主。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">全新 Range Rover 標配四輪轉向系統，在提升高速行駛的穩定性時，更能改善低速行駛的靈活度，適應不同的道路狀況。Range Rover 的電子式後軸轉向角多達 7 度，更會於低速行駛時與前輪反向轉動，使轉向半徑小於 11m；而在高速行駛時，後軸會與前輪會保持同向轉動，可提高穩定性和舒適度。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Range Rover 提供多種電能性能，包括 440 匹及 510 匹馬力的插電式混合動力（PHEV）系統，其純電續航力達 100 公里，每公里的二氧化碳排放量更低於 30 克。PHEV 使用直列六缸 Ingenium 引擎，搭載 31.8kWh 電能的 38.2kWh 的鋰離子電池，以及 105kW 的內置傳動系統電動摩打，時速可高達 140 公里；P510e 的 0-100 公里/小時加速只需 5.6 秒。而 P530 搭載雙渦輪增壓 V8 引擎，較上一代 Range Rover V8 的效率提高了 17%</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171439-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1106784" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171439-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171439-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171439-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171439-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171439-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171439-2048x1153.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171406-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1106779" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171406-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171406-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171406-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171406-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171406-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/20220602_171406-2048x1153.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">2022 新車參考價:</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">The New Range Rover P400 SWB HSE： HK$ 2,488,000 起</p><p