</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>神人改裝 2cm 激薄 PS5    可流暢玩到《Horizon Forbidden West》</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/25/sony-ps5-light/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=sony-ps5-light</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[王希雯]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jun 2022 03:18:13 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[PS5]]></category><category><![CDATA[改造]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1105903</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Sony 推出 PS5 接近兩年時間，早前宣佈已經解決了晶片及零件短缺的問題，Sony 決定加大 PS5 的產 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Sony 推出 PS5 接近兩年時間，早前宣佈已經解決了晶片及零件短缺的問題，Sony 決定加大 PS5 的產量。用戶們除了關注產量不足難以購買的問題，其中一個令人費思的問題是 PS5 體積比過往的遊戲機更大。最近就有一名外國知名改造大師 YouTuber DIY Perks 直接將 PS5 改造成接近 PS4 Slim 的超小體積，主機薄到只有 2cm。</p><p>YouTuber Matt 喜歡改造各種機械與電子器材，Matt 表示 PS5 是 Sony 有史以來最大的遊戲機，但官方並沒有纖薄版，故期望自己能夠自己拆解、組裝成易於收納的纖薄版 PS5 。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1105931 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.15.27-694x473.png" alt="" width="694" height="473" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.15.27-694x473.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.15.27-1280x873.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.15.27-768x524.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.15.27-1536x1047.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.15.27-2048x1396.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=he6xyl_MHXY">DIY Perks</a></p><p>最後，Matt 的確成功製作一個 2 cm 超薄主機，但在最初的遊戲測試過程中，因為電源過熱導致主機燒掉。後來他換上新主板，監測整體溫度變化，才成功運行整部超薄版 PS5 ，同時亦成功利用超薄版 PS5 進行 Sony 的《Horizon Forbidden West》遊戲。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1105924 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.07.26-694x325.png" alt="" width="694" height="325" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.07.26-694x325.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.07.26-1280x599.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.07.26-768x359.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.07.26-1536x719.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.07.26-2048x958.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1105923 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.07.36-694x348.png" alt="" width="694" height="348" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.07.36-694x348.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.07.36-1280x642.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.07.36-768x385.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.07.36-1536x770.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.07.36-2048x1027.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1105928 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.12.45-694x376.png" alt="" width="694" height="376" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.12.45-694x376.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.12.45-1280x693.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.12.45-768x416.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-20-下午 7.