</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>日本網民發明「零接觸」捕蟲神器，被商家睇中正式商品化</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/25/news-4/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=news-4</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jun 2022 03:06:09 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1106707</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>相信大家都曾在房間裡遇見昆蟲，但不想殺掉它的經歷。近早有日媒報道，社交媒體上出現了一項新產品，其不用徒手觸碰昆 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>相信大家都曾在房間裡遇見昆蟲，但不想殺掉它的經歷。近早有日媒報道，社交媒體上出現了一項新產品，其不用徒手觸碰昆蟲都可以捉到並釋放，成為網絡熱話。</p><p>此產品由日本大學的學生發明，該結構由是兩個部分打開的盒子簡單組合而成。當看到牆壁上有昆蟲時，只要拉開盒子的一部分，然後蓋著昆蟲並關上盒子，再到合適的地方打開盒子放掉昆蟲便可。過程不需不接觸昆蟲的情況下也能完美捕捉。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1106796 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.34-694x421.png" alt="" width="694" height="421" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.34-694x421.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.34-1280x777.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.34-768x466.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.34-1536x933.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.34-2048x1243.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1106797 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.42-694x380.png" alt="" width="694" height="380" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.42-694x380.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.42-1280x700.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.42-768x420.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.42-1536x840.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.42-2048x1120.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1106798 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.52-694x407.png" alt="" width="694" height="407" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.52-694x407.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.52-1280x751.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.52-768x451.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.52-1536x901.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-25-05.45.52-2048x1201.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（圖片來源：<span class="s2"><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MbCQWDyc9pg">ANNnewsCH</a>）</span></p><p>該產品在社交平臺 TikTok 後總瀏覽量超過 700 萬次，好評如潮，有不少玩家看到影片後表示希望擁有此工具，不想壓死蟲子、相讓蟲子活下去等評論。</p><p>產品被旭電機化成看準商機，其開發科長森內宗太表示，殺蟲劑和殺蟲產品有很多，但是從放生的角度出發的產品卻很少。旭電機化成經過內部反覆研究後，決定以 550 日元（約＄32 元港幣）的價格出售，並於四個月已售出超過 5,000 個。</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料</span><span class="s2">來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MbCQWDyc9pg">ANNnewsCH</a></span></p><p class="p2">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohid