</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>中國 31 項直播主行為規範，違者可能被永久封殺</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/25/chinas-top-media/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=chinas-top-media</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jun 2022 03:01:31 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1106661</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>國家廣電總局核下的文化和旅遊部日前就網絡主播行為制訂規範，列出多達 31 項禁止在直播節目上出現的行為，當中禁 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>國家廣電總局核下的文化和旅遊部日前就網絡主播行為制訂規範，列出多達 31 項禁止在直播節目上出現的行為，當中禁示出現歪曲中國傳統文化，以及利用偽造技術對國家領導人或英雄烈士進行篡改等內容，目的為促進網絡空間健康。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1106666 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.53.34-694x306.png" alt="" width="694" height="306" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.53.34-694x306.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.53.34-1280x564.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.53.34-768x339.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.53.34-1536x677.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.53.34-2048x903.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（圖片來源：<a href="http://www.nrta.gov.cn/art/2022/6/22/art_113_60757.html">國家廣播電視總局</a>）</p><p>中國政法大學傳播法研究中心副主任朱偉接受《環球時報》採訪時表示，規範內列出了 31 條比以前更詳細、具體的禁止行為，能明確向直播主指導直播期間的行為。朱偉又指，這些規範涉及直播行業相關的法律法規，例如未成年人保護和網絡安全法。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1106667 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.54.01-694x376.png" alt="" width="694" height="376" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.54.01-694x376.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.54.01-1280x693.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.54.01-768x416.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.54.01-1536x832.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-24-12.54.01-2048x1109.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（圖片來源：<a href="http://www.nrta.gov.cn/art/2022/6/22/art_113_60757.html">國家廣播電視總局</a>）</p><p>如有網絡主播違反有關規定，可能會被永久封殺，並將其列入「黑名單」或「警告名單」，更不能更換賬號或更換平臺再次進行直播活動。</p><p>除了針對直播節目內容的行為規範，有關規定亦提到，直播主還需如實申報收入並依法納稅。另外如直播內容牽及醫療衞生、財經金融、法律、教育等範疇，主播應有相應執業資質，並需要向直播平臺作申報。</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料</span><span class="s2">來源：<a href="https://www.globaltimes.cn/page/202206/1268814.shtml">globaltimes</a></span></p><p class="p2">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
